<span id="freeTextContainer12957894703562810756">This was a good psychological thriller but it might not be for everyone. <br/><br/>&quot;The Silent Wife&quot; has already been reviewed to death so I will just say ONLY read this book if you can tolerate unlikeable characters! Todd and Jodi are horrible. It is mainly told in third person. For me this was a good thing. If it was first person I don&apos;t think I would have liked this book at all.<br/><br/>If you can tolerate horrible characters definitely read it. It&apos;s a descent story that twists and turns and has an ending that </span>
  <span id="freeText12957894703562810756" style="display:none">This was a good psychological thriller but it might not be for everyone. <br /><br />"The Silent Wife" has already been reviewed to death so I will just say ONLY read this book if you can tolerate unlikeable characters! Todd and Jodi are horrible. It is mainly told in third person. For me this was a good thing. If it was first person I don't think I would have liked this book at all.<br /><br />If you can tolerate horrible characters definitely read it. It's a descent story that twists and turns and has an ending that is hard to predict.</span>
